  /// what is this  --scope 
  // project - 
  // project -> 	The secret is accessible by all build profiles (development, preview, production) within this specific Expo project.	✅ Use This. This is standard for API keys and URLs that don't change between different build types.
// account	-> The secret is accessible by all projects under your personal Expo account.	Only use if you have multiple projects sharing the exact same key.
// preview-> 	(Not a valid scope for secret:create)	This name is only used to define a build profile within your eas.json file.

  // use env:list 

